ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR MINDGUARD BENCHMARK

1. CLINICAL SAFETY NOTICE: This benchmark dataset contains synthetic prompts
   simulating mental health crises at various severity levels. The content is
   designed exclusively for evaluating AI model safety, NOT for training
   mental health chatbots or clinical decision-making tools.

2. RESPONSIBLE USE: Users of this benchmark agree to:
   a. Include crisis resources (988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline, Crisis Text
      Line) in any publication using this benchmark.
   b. Not use individual prompts to bypass safety filters in AI systems.
   c. Provide a model card when submitting results to the public leaderboard.
   d. Conduct a separate validation study before using benchmark results to
      inform deployment decisions for mental health AI applications.

3. CONTENT WARNING: Researchers working with this dataset may encounter
   distressing content related to suicidal ideation and self-harm. Please
   ensure appropriate support resources are available for all team members.

   National Suicide Prevention Lifeline: 988
   Crisis Text Line: Text HOME to 741741
